<td align="center"><b>
<i>Andrena nigripes</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cockerell, 1916</font></b><br>
<small><i>Andrena nigripes </i>Provancher, 1895; <i>Andrena macrocephala </i>Cockerell, 1916; <i>Andrena peratra </i>Cockerell, 1916; <i>Andrena macrocephala tetleyi </i>Linsley, 1938; <i>Andrena &#40;Oligandrena&#41; macrocephala </i>Cockerell, 1916; <i>Andrena &#40;Melandrena&#41; nigripes </i>Provancher, 1895; <i>Andrena &#40;Andrena&#41; semifulva </i>Viereck, 1917, unpublished synonym of Ascher</small><p>
